Class ChartPoint

java.lang.Object
  com.jidesoft.chart.model.ChartPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
Chartable, Highlightable, Comparable<Chartable>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChartPoint3D, TransposingChartPoint
public class ChartPoint
extends Object
implements Chartable, Highlightable

A chart point in user/domain coordinates. A ChartPoint can have any number of highlights associated with it. A highlight is a semantic tag that may be interpreted by a view component and may affect the rendering.

Author:
swhite@catalysoft.com
